description:
Danny welcomes Hannah Brown (host of Brown-Eyed Jewnicorn podcast and NOT current Bachelorette) to Everything Iconic to recap this week's Southern Charm. They also discuss the #RHOC trailer, Brittany & Jax's wedding, Ryan Gosling's movies, Cher, and MORE!


*To support this pod & access bonus episodes, visit Patreon.com/EverythingIconic
